    "It was also important to evaluate the performance of the KeyBERT model on different types of articles and domains, to ensure that it is generalizable and robust.In conclusion, using KeyBERT to extract keywords and generate topic names for articles involves preparing the data, setting up the KeyBERT model, extracting keywords, generating the topic name, and evaluating the results.",
